{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_04_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYが終了してしばらく経ち",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの新曲『SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me！』の正式リリースが決定したぞ",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　ありがとうございます！\n思い入れのある曲なのでリリースが決まって嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、曲が完成したばかりなのに\nもう発売が決まるなんて早過ぎじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 18.676581461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでのライブがもの凄い反響だったんだ\nおかげでトントン拍子に話が進んだよ",
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね\n私達の歌がそんなに話題になるなんて嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 30.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　みんなにもこのことを知らせなきゃ！\nそれじゃあ私はこれで――",
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待った\n新曲のリリースに向けてさくらに一つ頼みがあるんだ",
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}